ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v22.datatype

Class CM_RMC

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractType
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractComposite
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v22.datatype.CM_RMC
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Composite, Type, Visitable, Serializable

    public class CM_RMC
extends AbstractComposite

    Represents an HL7 CM_RMC (Room Coverage) data type. This type consists of the following components:

    • room type (ID)
    • amount type (ID)
    • coverage amount (NM)
